sources.description:
Beware the Bayou Moon: where humanity meets horror.
In the picturesque Louisiana bayou, a sheriff uncovers a string of brutal murders, but his hunt for a killer takes a hair-raising turn when evidence points to a suspected werewolf on the loose

Original title: Moon of the Wolf (1972)

This film has English, Portuguese & Spanish audio options, and is subtitled in many languages.

Director: Daniel Petrie
Writers: Alvin Sapinsley, Les Whitten
Stars: David Janssen, Barbara Rush, Bradford Dillman  
Genres: Cult Classic, Horror, Thriller
